  "prompt": "What are some good dance club songs?",
  "response": "Dance club songs are all about high energy, catchy beats, and infectious rhythms that get people moving. Here\u2019s a list of some popular and timeless tracks across different eras and genres that are guaranteed to light up the dance floor:\n\n### Classic Dance Hits:\n1. **Daft Punk - \"One More Time\"**  \n2. **Deee-Lite - \"Groove Is in the Heart\"**  \n3. **Madonna - \"Vogue\"**  \n4. **Michael Jackson - \"Don\u2019t Stop \u2019Til You Get Enough\"**  \n5. **Cher - \"Believe\"**  \n\n### 2000s Club Anthems:\n1. **Rihanna ft. Calvin Harris - \"We Found Love\"**  \n2. **Lady Gaga - \"Bad Romance\"**  \n3. **David Guetta ft. Sia - \"Titanium\"**  \n4. **Cascada - \"Everytime We Touch\"**  \n5. **Kylie Minogue - \"Can\u2019t Get You Out of My Head\"**  \n\n### EDM Bangers:\n1. **Zedd ft. Foxes - \"Clarity\"**  \n2. **Swedish House Mafia - \"Don\u2019t You Worry Child\"**  \n3. **Calvin Harris - \"Summer\"**  \n4. **Martin Garrix - \"Animals\"**  \n5. **Avicii - \"Wake Me Up\"**  \n\n### House and Tech Hits:\n1. **Disclosure - \"Latch\"**  \n2. **Duke Dumont - \"Ocean Drive\"**  \n3. **Fisher - \"Losing It\"**  \n4. **Sonny Fodera & Dom Dolla - \"Moving Blind\"**  \n5. **Green Velvet - \"La La Land\"**  \n\n### Current Pop/Club Bangers:\n1. **Dua Lipa - \"Levitating\"**  \n2. **Doja Cat - \"Say So\"**  \n3. **The Weeknd - \"Blinding Lights\"**  \n4. **Beyonc\u00e9 - \"Break My Soul\"**  \n5. **Kim Petras & Sam Smith - \"Unholy\"**  \n\n### Throwback Dance Tracks:\n1. **Robin S. - \"Show Me Love\"**  \n2. **Daft Punk - \"Around the World\"**  \n3. **Stardust - \"Music Sounds Better With You\"**  \n4. **Modjo - \"Lady (Hear Me Tonight)\"**  \n5. **Moloko - \"Sing It Back\"**  \n\n### Global/International Hits:\n1. **Major Lazer ft. MO & DJ Snake - \"Lean On\"**  \n2. **Burak Yeter - \"Tuesday\"**  \n3. **Drake - \"One Dance\"**  \n4. **Black Coffee & David Guetta ft. Delilah Montagu - \"Drive\"**  \n5. **Rosal\u00eda - \"Juro Que\"**  \n\nThese songs span a variety of styles, so you can mix and match depending on the vibe of the crowd. Let the beats drop and the dance floor heat up! \ud83c\udfb6\ud83d\udc83\ud83d\udd7a",
